<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Secret Intelligence Service, often known as MI6, collects Britain’s foreign intelligence. It provides the government with a global covert capability to promote and defend the national security and economic well-being of the country. SIS works with the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office ."@en .
